text: Food Network is an American food-themed television network headquartered in New York City. It launched in November 1993.http://www.foodnetwork.com The Food Network has many shows. Some of them are: * Iron Chef America * Chopped * Kids Baking Championship * 30 Minute Meals * Diners, Drive-Ins & Dives * The Next Food Network Star * Good Eats == References == Category:1993 establishments in the United States Category:Cable television Category:1990s establishments in New York (state)
